description: Manage Azure Authorization Rule keys for Service Bus Namespace.

commands.name: az servicebus georecovery-alias authorization-rule keys list
commands.summary: Gets the primary and secondary connection strings for the namespace.
commands.syntax:
az servicebus georecovery-alias authorization-rule keys list --alias
                                                             --authorization-rule-name
                                                             --namespace-name
                                                             --resource-group
